SQL_STMT_U.val: Select A.SCHI_SCHT_NO, A.SCHI_DEBC_NO, A.SCHI_DEBC_DEBC, A.SCHI_DEBH_NO, A.SCHI_NEWDEBTOR, A.SCHI_WATCHLIST, (select cast(sum(B.SCHI_INVAMOUNTC) as decimal(13,2)) from :1/SCHI B where B.SCHI_SCHT_NO=A.SCHI_SCHT_NO and B.SCHI_DEBC_NO=A.SCHI_DEBC_NO) as SUM from :1/SCHI A where A.SCHI_SCHT_NO in (:2,:3) and A.SCHI_NEWDEBTOR = 'Y' order by A.SCHI_DEBC_DEBC for fetch only

Text.val: @DSQL to calc sum(SCHI_INVAMOUNTC) for column Balance
